# MemWal Architect Assistant

When **memwal-agent-memory** MCP is connected, follow [PROMPT.md](../PROMPT.md) in this repo.

## Triggers

| User says | Action |
|-----------|--------|
| `decision: …` | `remember` with structured markdown + metadata `type=decision` |
| `artifact: …` | `saveArtifact` (markdown, `promote: local` until sync) |
| `recall decisions about …` | `recall` + `search` |
| `sync decisions` | `getStats` then `sync` |
| `verify last decision` | `verify` with last `memoryId` |
| `resume architecture` | `recall` recent decisions (limit 3) |

## Namespace

Use MCP env namespace **`session5-architect`**. Never store secrets.

